137
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,120
[No insulin left in the fridge.]

138
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,640
[I'll take you to the hospital tomorrow.]

139
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:32,600
Your fasting blood sugar

140
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,360
