141
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,760
are already past the danger zone.

142
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:35,560
You need to be hospitalized.

143
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,000
Listen to the doc.

144
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:43,080
I don't want to.

145
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,560
You should listen to the doctor.

146
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:45,920
Can't believe I fall

147
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,280
for your words about the insulin.

148
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,640
Ma'am,

149
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,880
at this stage,

150
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,120
hospitalization is a must.

151
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:53,720
If you don't control your sugar,

152
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,200
complications can easily arise.

153
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,520
That would be dangerous.

154
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,720
Is it that serious?

155
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,760
Are you worried about the cost?

156
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:01,840
Well, most of the

157
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,000
hospitalization expenses

158
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,040
can be reimbursed.

159
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:05,480
Including the insulin.

160
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,720
Once

161
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,200
your blood sugar stabilizes,

162
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,200
you can be discharged.

163
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,720
I'll also prescribe two weeks'

164
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,240
worth of insulin for you to take away.

165
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,200
Two whole weeks'

166
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,520
worth of insulin

167
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:17,160
to take home?

168
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,000
Right.

169
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,280
Saves a lot of money.

170
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,720
Fine, admit me.

171
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,720
That's right.

172
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,200
I'll write you a form.

173
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,640
Here, take them back.

174
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:31,160
Thanks.

175
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,320
Patient's name?

176
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:36,840
Huang Shufen.

177
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,200
Here.

178
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,120
Paid the fees.

179
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,440
Keep these papers.

180
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,240
Huang Shufen!

181
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,720
How dare you call me by my name?

182
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,120
