183
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,280
Let me see.

184
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:22,960
Let me see.

185
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,960
Where did you get this?

186
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:27,560
From the cabinet.

187
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,120
You can't eat this.

188
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,120
Go check them.

189
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:38,520
Where's my ID?

190
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,280
What are you doing?

191
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,160
Take a photo for memories.

192
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:50,080
November 8th, 1946.

193
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,320
Scorpio.

194
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:52,960
What?

195
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:55,160
Zodiac. Scorpio.

196
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,120
So?

197
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,000
Scorpios are kinda grudging.

198
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,320
Grudging?

199
00:09:58,880 --> 00:09:59,560
Huh.

200
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,600
When was my grandpa's birthday?

201
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,280
What now?

202
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,040
Just curious if you two were meant to be.

203
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:09,960
Huh?

204
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:17,840
July 4th, 1941.

205
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:18,880
Cancer.

206
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,360
