230
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:03,560
Don't jinx it!

231
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,600
Alright, alright.

232
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,680
Go home.

233
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,920
Pass me the remote.

234
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,920
