236
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,680
You wouldn't understand, kiddo.

237
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,840
Dealing with animals

238
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:22,080
is much easier than dealing with people.

239
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:25,720
Got it.

240
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,560
Remote, the remote.

241
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,640
Need to get new pigeon grit.

242
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:32,720
Head to

243
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:34,720
the back of the flower-and-bird market,

244
00:11:34,920 --> 00:11:36,720
look for Old Man Qian,

245
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,520
and buy it from him.

246
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,080
I know exactly how many

247
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,280
pigeons I have.

248
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,360
If even one's missing when I get back,

249
00:11:44,520 --> 00:11:45,280
I'll beat you black and blue.

250
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,720
I love eating pigeon meat.

251
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,720
Say that again, I'll hold a grudge.

252
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,920
[I brought all this for you two.]

253
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,520
