259
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,240
So many snacks.

260
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,720
My mom bought all these?

261
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,120
Don't lie to me.

262
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:12,520
Maybe they were just

263
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,280
free samples

264
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,360
with the fruit she bought.

265
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,440
Your mom misses you a lot.

266
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:20,120
She's just tough on the outside.

267
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:22,520
Oh, right.

268
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,080
You were looking for a job, right?

269
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:25,320
So

270
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,640
